{
  "stem": "24466.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he told me about this, that Bialystok was already taken because they were advancing very quickly, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they're liberating part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they-- they haven't got, unfortunately, the-- the specialist in the leather industry, that most, they were Jews, and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And unfortunately, there are not anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They are not existing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you are willing to go to-- from-- to leave Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I didn't took up, not the Lithuanian citizenship, not the Russian citizenship, and I was a Polish citizenship.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, by all means, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The idea was to be as close to my father to find out what happens to my family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] a general one, from [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He become-- when Bialystok was liberated, he become the [NON-ENGLISH]-- not the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I don't what-- how to explain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a leader, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the-- is a-- is a governor, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A mayor, a governor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A governor.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A governor of Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came twice or three times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was coming to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Vilna, having a talk to me, having a talk to the boss.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My director wasn't from the-- from the factory wasn't my boss.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the boss, mine was [INAUDIBLE], and he was the Minister of Light Industry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a fight going on there to relieve me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he relieved me to go, to leave Lithuania, to leave my position, and to go with-- to Bialystok to [INAUDIBLE] to that [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
